STATEMENT_TEXT: SELECT STORE_SALES.SS_WHOLESALE_COST, STORE_RETURNS.SR_NET_LOSS FROM STORE_SALES INNER JOIN STORE_RETURNS ON STORE_RETURNS.SR_TICKET_NUMBER = STORE_SALES.SS_TICKET_NUMBER AND STORE_RETURNS.SR_ITEM_SK = STORE_SALES.SS_ITEM_SK WHERE STORE_SALES.SS_STORE_SK = 2 AND STORE_RETURNS.SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK = 2451680

SELECT Q1.SS_WHOLESALE_COST AS "SS_WHOLESALE_COST", Q2.SR_NET_LOSS AS "SR_NET_LOSS" FROM DB2INST1.STORE_SALES AS Q1, DB2INST1.STORE_RETURNS AS Q2 WHERE (Q2.SR_TICKET_NUMBER = Q1.SS_TICKET_NUMBER) AND (Q2.SR_ITEM_SK = Q1.SS_ITEM_SK) AND (Q2.SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK = 2451680) AND (Q1.SS_STORE_SK = 2)
